_sText: The idea for this map just came to me. The original gg_sl_bend used custom blue textures. I think for some people the blue was too much, so I retextured the map, and improved lighting. This map has buy points so that you can play it as an aim or fy map if you wish. About modifying this map This map is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-Noncommercial 3.0 license. (When making a modification to this map, please give some sort of attribution to me. If you modify the map, please rename the map to anything other than gg_sl_bend-x to avoid confusion with this original map.) You can download the map's vmf file here.
